{"tid":1168123,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"求教!!點追工程貨款尾數??","createTime":"2019-05-23T12:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T16:13:13.000Z","uid":185185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"15ed01676553cd5b2c7432b5f01a74efa8f64272","tid":1168123,"uid":185185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"本身同上家開二前簽左報價。工程起左貨, 應收到合約金額100%。<br />\n<br />\n點知前兩個月上家俾大判趕走埋, 欠40萬左右未找。可以點追? 找收數公司定同大判傾?點搞好? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有經驗的巴打請教路, 感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04439b613c39e6482a0d6017eb0d2f1574baf056","tid":1168123,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:01:47.000Z","msg":"問大判啦，趕得佢走即姐未比曬錢佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你幫大判起到貨，直接比錢你都好合情合理"},{"pid":"b5ceecf2408a0ce0989c4e8c985ac11b6475fea3","tid":1168123,"uid":185185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"起左貨了, D野仲好靚。有晒相片。"},{"pid":"5e24fa7b0188f276152486c7380b9aec3afd523f","tid":1168123,"uid":51041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"搵隊去佢公司門口拉banner <br />\n有汗出<br />\n冇糧出<br />\n等等"},{"pid":"b623cb34e001bccd30a7ce4fd6053afc9a2b3c29","tid":1168123,"uid":185185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"法律途徑上有冇計?"},{"pid":"dd91014352825291012d2b72e52b45d92a16d4d6","tid":1168123,"uid":170389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"三沙會唔識大判site agent?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2a8f65ea668f20996ba56e2f5725f441f69f9e","tid":1168123,"uid":185185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd91014352825291012d2b72e52b45d