4d747","tid":1168123,"uid":185185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"一開始只係我公司同X公司(俾人趕走又未找數個間)之間有協議, X簽左我公司份報價<br />\n<br />\n兩個月左右前, 開始按進度收數, 冇錢俾仲俾人趕走埋。唯有去現場找大判傾。大判口頸講會處理。狂追都冇...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"大判最多咪代出2個月工人糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe86e8865e94c91f8c1250e98eff84ba90f28c1","tid":1168123,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"哩d 野最撚乞人憎, 條數又唔係大, 但係你要搵律師搞鳩佢你自己都一身煩. 所以同香港人做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ebc2be8c88abb350a3d802b794f00cb8e77b9cc","tid":1168123,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"收數公司work不過收得好貴<br />\n<br />\n上年有單2x萬 收番 18萬  4萬中介費"},{"pid":"b00e88097a2a2757f0ad4e485eff7cdaf89257c3","tid":1168123,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:49:36.000Z","msg":"拖硬你啦<br />\n找唔找真係隨佢喜歡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd4544e319a0bd1159d69a09811efdd0b922ece","tid":1168123,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bdb2a14d355e6cd52a4d8e87ae0a72246f00565","tid":1168123,"uid":197569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b623cb34e001bccd30a7ce4fd6053afc9a2b3c29","tid":1168123,"uid":185185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:12:24.000Z","msg":"法律途徑上有冇計?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:16:22.000Z","msg":"你同大判沒合約，點追？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"大判要代出糧喎雖然得一個月"},{"pid":"b4c1891bbe9a6402370ad101bda424fcdc3d2ff5","tid":1168123,"uid":185185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇巴打有其他意見?"},{"pid":"c10ee068dfb089b39b7400f1b0c85e82b92d6322","tid":1168123,"uid":244281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T14:44:21.000Z","msg":"1. 公司：<br />\n(1) 大判<br />\n(2) 二判（你上家）<br />\n(3) 三沙（你公司）<br />\n<br />\n2. 合約：<br />\n(1) 大判同二判之間（假設你唔知合約內容）<br />\n(2) 二判同三沙之間（你知道合約內容）<br />\n<br />\n3. 事實：<br />\n(1) 三沙起左貨<br />\n(2) 前兩個月二判俾大判趕走<br />\n(3) 二判欠40萬左右未找比三沙（應該唔係想講大判欠40萬左右未找二判？）<br />\n<br />\n4. 問：<br />\n(1) 三沙可以點追返40萬<br />\n<br />\n5. 斷估：<br />\n(1) 先追二判，有 Privity of contract，三沙好難直接告大判。<br />\n(2) 如果二判失蹤，再追大判。<br />\n(3) 引用合約條文書面要求付款。注意大判有冇比錢二判，同二判需唔需要比錢三判冇關（除非有Back to Back / Paid when Paid 條款）。<br />\n(4) 如果唸住打官司，預左有排玩，贏左最多拎返7成。打官司之前查左對方有冇資產先。<br />\n(5) 如果唔想煩，入小額錢債拎返7萬5算數。<br />\n(6) 如果工人有大判登記/出入紀錄，可考慮有汗出冇糧出。政府盤尤其有效。<br />\n(7) 如果係賣貨，可要求問大判取回貨物（incomplete transfer of good title, tort of conversion?）<br />\n(8) Prove unjust enrichment<br />\n(9) 其實二判比大判趕走，二判點解唔告大判？定係其實係二判Repudiate Contact？ <br />\n(10) 個人意見：40萬請律師追 = 倒錢落海<br />\n<br />\n6. 其他參考資料：<br />\n香港Case Law <a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fsearch%2Fsearch.jsp&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=ece7143c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/search/search.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你。"}]}